00:38:29.860 --> 00:38:32.110
There's fear.

00:38:32.110 --> 00:38:34.850
But then I'm like,
there's ignorance.

00:38:34.850 --> 00:38:37.742
But then, oh wait, I
don't want to judge others

00:38:37.742 --> 00:38:39.200
when I'm trying to
understand them.

00:38:39.200 --> 00:38:42.270
That's why I'm watching this
spectacle in the first place.

00:38:42.270 --> 00:38:45.912
But I can't get
past that judgment.

00:38:45.912 --> 00:38:47.370
SHARON SALZBERG:
You want to start?

00:38:47.370 --> 00:38:50.350
You want me to start?

00:38:50.350 --> 00:38:52.190
PHOENIX SOLEIL: Why
don't you start?

00:38:52.190 --> 00:38:53.900
AUDIENCE: And I'm
looking for tools

00:38:53.900 --> 00:38:57.270
to get past it, because
