00:53:20.680 --> 00:53:22.470
they have for their family.

00:53:22.470 --> 00:53:26.840
And I will see the
tenderness that they

00:53:26.840 --> 00:53:29.300
have for some of the
people they care about

00:53:29.300 --> 00:53:34.600
and the lengths they have
gone to protect and to care.

00:53:34.600 --> 00:53:37.250
And then sometimes,
there will be something

00:53:37.250 --> 00:53:41.540
